==English==
===Etymology===
A Native American (Sioux) saying used to emphasize the desirability of an honorable death. It is credited to the Oglala Sioux war leader Crazy Horse (Tasunka Witko) [[http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Crazy_Horse]]

=====In Science Fiction=====
It has since been attributed as a [[Klingon]] saying to emphasize similar meaning.

